      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering atmospheric induction through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain is flawlessly sorted, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a tight variable M differential lock. The chassis remains rigid with no signs of fatigue, and the suspension geometry maintains its factory-spec compliance. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this car offers a linear powerband that pulls aggressively to an 8,000 RPM redline, representing a collector-grade investment for the purist driver.",
